+<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/OTBA> <http://data.bgs.ac.uk/ref/Lexicon/hasBroaderPredominantAge> <http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Geochronology/Division/T> .
+<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/SHHI> <http://data.bgs.ac.uk/ref/Lexicon/hasBroaderPredominantAge> <http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Geochronology/Division/T> .
+<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/CRNS> <http://data.bgs.ac.uk/ref/Lexicon/hasLateralEquivalent> <http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/H1632> .
