+<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/KECR> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Obsolete name. Stratified bedrock. Occurs onshore. Deposited during the Holkerian Substage (Carboniferous Period) (343-337 Ma BP)."@en .
