+<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/SCSL> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Limestone. Stratified bedrock. Occurs onshore. Deposited during the Asbian Substage (Carboniferous Period) (337-330.9 Ma BP)."@en .
