+<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/SHHI> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Mudstone, sandstone and siltstone. Stratified bedrock. Occurs offshore. Deposited during the Early Triassic Epoch (Triassic Period) (251.9-246.7 Ma BP)."@en .
